data.title: list experience with Southwest Airlines
data.meta_description: Sign up now through May 31 to take advantage of this promotional offer and receive A-list status for 90 days.
data.text:
UT Health San Antonio has partnered with Southwest to give employees A-List status on their next trip. Any UT Health San Antonio employee is eligible to enroll, and this benefit can be earned and enjoyed for both business and leisure travel.

A-List status members enjoy priority boarding, priority check-in and security lane access, same-day standby, earning rewards bonus and more. Sign up now through May 31 to take advantage of this promotional offer and receive A-list status for 90 days. To register, visit: www.southwest.com/businesstierexperience/.
